sources.description:
LAND OF FURY - Tough woodsmen fighting for giant trees and gorgeous women!
Loggers Jeff Collins and Boomer Benson compete for a mail-order bride by means of a timber-cutting contest.

Original title: Thunder in the Pines (1949) AKA: Green Gold

Colorized version https://youtu.be/eo-KIavO4PA

Director: Robert Gordon
Writers: Jo Pagano, Maurice Tombragel
Stars: George Reeves, Ralph Byrd, Greg McClure
Genres: Drama, Romance, Western
